    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to acquire a truly showroom-condition masterpiece. This vehicle has been meticulously curated and maintained to an exacting standard, offering an unrivaled aesthetic and mechanical profile for the discerning driver. Every surface, from the flawless factory finish to the pristine interior, reflects a life of climate-controlled storage and preventative care. This is a collector-grade specimen that delivers the same presence and performance as the day it left the assembly line. Fully documented and rigorously inspected for absolute peace of mind.",
      "price": 48900.0,
